data-triple-N3.o: "Nottingham Forest Football Club is an English Football club based in West Bridgford, Nottingham that currently plays in the Football League Championship. Forest have been based at the City Ground since 1898. Founded in 1865, the club were founder members of the Football Alliance in 1889 and joined the Football League in 1892."@en
